Ankha

08/22/2024 at 07:15:51 undefined
Pocket Paradise (Church of Pocket)

Abuse 1 skill aoe to hit people behind cover during laning. Use abilities to flash farm neutrals and lane creeps. when you use teleport to a ghost and you are in the suitcase the suitcase damage appears where you end up. So if you want to damage enemies near your current location end the suitcase first. (suitcase = 3rd ability). You are very quick at stealing the small camp from enemies during laning stage if you get the opportunity. Silencing glyph is really strong early game to burst down people. Especially if they want to use abilities to escape. high velocity item works on skill 1. maxed skill 1 is a buff and not a debuff so just try to hit any enemies. It also cannot be stacked more than 4 times so echo shard/refresher are not good. Early 2nd and 3rd skill to level 2 for the 80 dmg is good for farming and should be prio. If enemy has healing an early level 2 ultimate is good to reduce that.
